Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, {\alpha&HFF&}it went smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, it went smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have done what you told me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T, {\alpha&HFF&}that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T, that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:03:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have received all the messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also have one thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have confirmed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah? {\alpha&HFF&}An email?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah? An email?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she wants to meet you she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so envious of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! {\alpha&HFF&}That's to say that Mikami has confirmed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That's to say that Mikami has confirmed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I need to do now is to wait for Near to request a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, {\alpha&HFF&}this is my victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, this is my victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have predicted how you are going to move very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Gevanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, I have checked the notebook and confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami has written down a page per day for the last three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The names on them match the victims. Mikami did not act differently as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. {\alpha&HFF&}Well then, let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Well then, let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I want to show you regarding the Kira Incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wasn't I regarded as Kira by you? {\alpha&HFF&}You should not want to reveal to me what you look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wasn't I regarded as Kira by you? You should not want to reveal to me what you look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have to reveal my face to show you what I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, by revealing my face, I can reveal something to you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, we will be able to put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to put an end to this wrong idea you have of me quickly as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near is doing this to show that Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Light is Kira, he will be doing this to kill Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And before that, I would like to make an agreement with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Just spell out whatever requests you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, all members from each team are to attend this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning, we will gather everyone who is after Kira at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my side, it will be like I told you. Four people including myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will make up the whole SPK team.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as for the abducted Mr. Mogi, we will bring him along, while releasing Amane without revealing where we are going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can confirm our release of Amane before moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near. {\alpha&HFF&}Roger that. With me included, we have a team of five over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near. Roger that. {\alpha&HFF&}With me included, we have a team of five over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near. Roger that. With me included, we have a team of five over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}with Mogi-san with you, I have only three other people with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... with Mogi-san with you, I have only three other people with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. {\alpha&HFF&}Well then, next will be deciding our meeting place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Well then, next will be deciding our meeting place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a Daikoku Wharf at the Southeast area. At the moment, it is not being used.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a place also known as "Yellow Box".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is good enough, we will proceed with the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that, Yagami Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, you should be able to do what you want to do as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing. I would like someone in the investigation team to bring the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all of you came over to meet me, there will be no one keeping guard on the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can promise you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not attempt to take the notebook away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To confirm that you are bringing the real one, and are indeed from the team,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will just need Mr. Aizawa's confirmation, and I will believe in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, please make sure someone other than L is carrying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still think that L is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, {\alpha&HFF&}but I will get to choose who carries it. Will that be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, but I will get to choose who carries it. {\alpha&HFF&}Will that be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, but I will get to choose who carries it. Will that be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we are only left with the day and date.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day and date? Time is the important factor here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mikami is doing his judgment from midnight, {\alpha&HFF&}he must have picked out his targets during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mikami is doing his judgment from midnight, he must have picked out his targets during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we take this time into consideration...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3 days after today, on the 28th, at 1pm. How is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1pm? {\alpha&HFF&}That's the time I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1pm? That's the time I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near knows how Mikami work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. On our side, any time is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, 3 days later at 1pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have predicted and read your moves. I am definitely going to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am quite busy today...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you're not staying until the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hands will be full over the next 2 to 3 days with police work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.89,0:09:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami and Takada have already been instructed on what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last instruction to kill Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke? There's an attacker!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-sama, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting away! After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-sama, let's get into NHN quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that! With this kind of attack, it will be dangerous inside NHN!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, it's better to get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-sama, please get on the bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-sama, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on the bike and get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A team and B team, stay around Takada-sama. Other teams, please go after the attacker in the car just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosh, I have confirmed her safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help Takada-sama into the number 7 car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This cannot be...! Takada-sama is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you hit Takada-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the attackers is armed with various weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takada Guard Team and the police are doing their best to find out where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-{\alpha&HFF&}This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Near again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... {\alpha&HFF&}He had arranged for us to meet in 3 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... He had arranged for us to meet in 3 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will he gain from something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, rather than saying Near is behind this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys have been waiting for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many guards does Takada have?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Since when is Japanese allowed to have possessions of those nice arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, you want to know where my accomplice has taken Takada, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't possibly fire at--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot. It's not like you were going to tell us a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going against Kira-sama is definitely a crime punishable by death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person... {\alpha&HFF&}is one of the people Yagami-kun told me to be especially careful of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person... is one of the people Yagami-kun told me to be especially careful of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello! {\alpha&HFF&}Mihael Keehl...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello! Mihael Keehl...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take off everything you are wearing and put them in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, this time, the abduction of Takada has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? {\alpha&HFF&}If that's the case, Mello...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? If that's the case, Mello...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. To tell you the truth, the guard that I sent has already confirmed it was done by Mello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the trouble my guard has caused, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, if it's you, can you get through to Mello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I do have a way to do that, Mello will not respond at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I take off my underwear, can you pass me the blanket?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Guard Team has taken down one of the accomplices of the kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are currently still tracking where Takada-sama is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it was no use after all, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... {\alpha&HFF&}Takada-san's phone is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Takada-san's phone is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With no way to get in contact with Takada, there's nothing other to do than to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no other way than this. {\alpha&HFF&}I have to be the one to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no other way than this. I have to be the one to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The identity of the man who was shot to death is still unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matt... {\alpha&HFF&}I got you killed... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matt... I got you killed... {\alpha&HFF&}sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matt... I got you killed... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she can contact me through her phone, that would mean... {\alpha&HFF&}she's gotten away from Mello... or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she can contact me through her phone, that would mean... she's gotten away from Mello... {\alpha&HFF&}or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she can contact me through her phone, that would mean... she's gotten away from Mello... or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun! {\alpha&HFF&}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now. Calm down and answer my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, the place. {\alpha&HFF&}Do you know where you are right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, the place. Do you know where you are right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am locked inside a truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were at the expressway, I did saw a signboard stating "Nagano". {\alpha&HFF&}Right now, we're in some building...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were at the expressway, I did saw a signboard stating "Nagano". Right now, we're in some building...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san. {\alpha&HFF&}You're Kira's spokeswoman. Do you remember how I told you the possibility that your life would be in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san. You're Kira's spokeswoman. {\alpha&HFF&}Do you remember how I told you the possibility that your life would be in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san. You're Kira's spokeswoman. Do you remember how I told you the possibility that your life would be in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In those situations, {\alpha&HFF&}I told you what you are supposed to do. Do you remember them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In those situations, I told you what you are supposed to do. {\alpha&HFF&}Do you remember them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In those situations, I told you what you are supposed to do. Do you remember them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The things that Yagami-kun told me to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have done them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:17:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I was stripped naked, I did not resist, but did what Yagami-kun said, and placed staying alive as my top priority...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have done them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, I have done everything you told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come quickly! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san, you know what to do from now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To do as much judgment as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, {\alpha&HFF&}but Yagami-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but Yagami-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa-san, Ide-san, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda-san will stay watch in HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as much judgment as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... {\alpha&HFF&}yes... I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... yes... {\alpha&HFF&}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... yes... I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that she is telling me this, means that she has taken out the kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, she must be in a state where she can't move around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakajima-kun, I am going to the actual scene of the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step on it. I've gotten her location.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on the freeway and head towards Karuizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's Karuizawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... that will take at least 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mello, and we don't know what he'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well. {\alpha&HFF&}Aizawa and Ide are still too careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well. Aizawa and Ide are still too careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just sat in the frontseats without me asking them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, I don't even have to do much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
